(355, 39, 26, 00355, 'Bosch Master CGF 800 S Power', '<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\">Control and Power Supply Unit<br /></span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\">&bull; Conference control without operator<br />&bull; Four selectable microphone modes and a &nbsp;&nbsp;test mode<br />&bull; Controls up to 50 contribution units<br />&bull; Interfaces the system with external audio &nbsp;&nbsp;equipment<br />&bull; Provides power for all system elements<br />&bull; Built-in listening facilities&nbsp;<br /><br />The Control and Power Supply Unit (CPSU) is the heart of a discussion system. This<br />versatile unit includes features for managing the number of active microphones and<br />determining the operating mode, without the need for a central operator. External<br />equipment can be connected to extend system possibilities. A built-in loudspeaker<br />allows the conference to be monitored (to allow a stenographer, for example, to take<br />notes on the conference).</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'default.png', 8000000, NULL, 0, '2017-05-13 07:44:21', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
