><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Monitor size and dots </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Wide, 3.2-in. (3:2) with approx. 1.04 million dots&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Brightness adjustment </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Manual (7 levels)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Electronic level </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Horizontal: 	1&deg; increments, &plusmn;6&deg;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Vertical:                   1&deg; increments, &plusmn;4&deg;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Interface languages </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">25&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Feature guide </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Displayable&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Camera System status display </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Provided&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>External Flash</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\">\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">E-TTL II autoflash EX-series Speedlites&nbsp;