><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Manual&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Sistem Metering</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\">\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1,005-pixel RGB sensor 3D Color Matrix Metering II&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Variable Center-weighted&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Spot AF&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Exposure Compensation</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\">\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">&plusmn;5 EV in increments of 1/3&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1/2&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>ISO Sensitivity</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">ISO: 100-1600 (expandable to 50-6400) </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Lowest Standard ISO Sensitivity </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">100 in steps of 1/3&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1/2&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1 EV&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Highest Standard ISO Sensitivity </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1600in steps of 1/3&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1/2&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1EV&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Lowest Expanded ISO Sensitivity </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Lo-1 (ISO 50 equivalent, in steps of 1/3, 1/2, 1 EV)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Highest Expanded ISO Sensitivity </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">HI-2 (ISO 6400 equivalent)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Expanded ISO Sensitivity Options </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Lo-1, (ISO-50 equivalent), in 1/3, 1/2 or 1 EV steps&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hi-1, (ISO-3200 equivalent), in 1/3, 1/2 or 1 EV steps&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hi-2, (ISO-6400 equivalent), 1 EV step&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Shutter</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">1/8000 - 30 sec, bulb&nbsp;</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>White Balance</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2