;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>White Balance</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\">\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Auto&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Daylight&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Shade&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Cloudy&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Tungsten Light&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">White Fluorescent Light&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Flash&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Custom&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Color Temperature setting&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Viewfinder</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\">\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Eye-level pentaprism&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Coverage : Vertical/Horizontal approx. 96%&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Magnification : Approx. 0.95x (-1m-1 with 50mm lens at infinity) / 27.0&deg; angle of view&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Eye Point : Approx. 22mm (At -1m-1 from eyepiece lens center)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Dioptric Adjustment Correction : -3.0 to +1.0m-1 (diopter)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>LCD Monitor</strong></span></td