rox. 0.71x&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Diopter Adjustment </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- 3.0 to +1.0 m&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>LCD Monitor</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\">\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Display Screen </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3\" Rear Screen   LCD (1040000)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Screen Coverage </span>\n<div>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">100%&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Internal Flash</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">No&nbsp;</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>External Flash</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Hot Shoe&nbsp;</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Live View</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Yes&nbsp;</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<