thium-Ion Battery Pack (7.2V, 1800mAh)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">AVC-DC400ST Stereo AV Cable&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">IFC-200U USB Interface Cable - 6.9\' (1.9 m)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">EOS Digital Solution Disk&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Camera Instruction Book&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Pocket Guide&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px; border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Lain-lain</strong></span></td>\n<td style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #E2E2E2;\" valign=\"top\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Termasuk  Lensa AF 24-105mm f/4L IS USM&nbsp;</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 'default.png', 0, NULL, 0, '2017-05-13 07:44:21', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
